 {"id":"bd-3vbf.4","title":"Design System: Icon/Emoji Vocabulary for Semantic Indicators","description":"## Background

beads_viewer uses rich iconography where every icon/emoji has semantic meaning:
- Status icons: 🟢 (open), 🔵 (progress), 🔴 (blocked), ⚫ (closed)
- Priority icons: 🔥 (critical), ⚡ (high), 🔹 (medium), ☕ (low), 💤 (minimal)
- Type icons: 🐛 (bug), ✨ (feature), 📋 (task), 🚀 (epic), 🧹 (chore)
- Action icons: ⛔ (blocked), 🔗 (linked), 📦 (depends), 🔍 (search)
- UI indicators: 📍 (anchor), 🕐 (history), ✓ (done), ✗ (failed)

Icons provide instant visual recognition without reading text.

## Implementation

Create icon constants in theme.rs:
```rust
pub mod icons {
    // Status
    pub const STATUS_OPEN: &str = "🟢";
    pub const STATUS_PROGRESS: &str = "🔵";
    pub const STATUS_BLOCKED: &str = "🔴";
    pub const STATUS_CLOSED: &str = "⚫";

    // Priority
    pub const PRIORITY_CRITICAL: &str = "🔥";
    pub const PRIORITY_HIGH: &str = "⚡";
    pub const PRIORITY_MEDIUM: &str = "🔹";
    pub const PRIORITY_LOW: &str = "☕";

    // Types
    pub const TYPE_ERROR: &str = "❌";
    pub const TYPE_WARNING: &str = "⚠️";
    pub const TYPE_INFO: &str = "ℹ️";
    pub const TYPE_SUCCESS: &str = "✓";

    // UI Elements
    pub const ARROW_RIGHT: &str = "→";
    pub const ARROW_LEFT: &str = "←";
    pub const BULLET: &str = "•";
    pub const CHECKBOX_ON: &str = "☑";
    pub const CHECKBOX_OFF: &str = "☐";
}
```

Also create RenderIcon helper function that combines icon + style.

## Justification

Icons:
- Provide instant recognition (faster than reading)
- Add visual interest and polish
- Create consistent visual language
- Work across languages

## Considerations

- Terminal emoji support varies
- Need fallback for non-emoji terminals
- Width calculation must handle emoji (usually 2 cells)

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] Icon constants for all semantic meanings
- [ ] RenderIcon helper function
- [ ] Fallback for terminals without emoji
- [ ] Demo screens use icons consistently

